reubendaniels pushed 26 commits to branch FHIR-22747. Commits by lmckenzi (9), jduteau (8), MLD1995 (3) and others (6).

  • FHIR-25128 - Corrected documentation in display-category terminology artifacts to refer to 'display', not 'text' (12b5e16)
  • FHIR-25478, FHIR-25599 - Added 'grid' group code to itemControl extension (7d821de)
  • Jiras #31511, #31510, #31351, (individual renamed to subject) #23028 (adding progress) (e25dc63)
  • Cleaning up codesystem files (bb90ace)
  • Merge pull request #1218 from HL7/glover-researchStudy (66fd6ad)
  • FHIR-27884 - Fixed parameter types for $questionnaire operation (b251978)
  • FHIR-29311 - Clarifications on readOnly and required (00a5007)
  • FHIR-25512 - Require names on variable extension (f03a153)
  • Merge branch 'master' of https://github.com/HL7/fhir (172fb18)
  • Mark useContext as TrialUse for Questionnaire (fe40089)
  • Merge pull request #1219 from HL7/Questionnaire-changes (e0d7159)
  • Added NutritionProduct to alphabetical list. (a369049)
  • Merge pull request #1220 from HL7/jd-nutritionproduct (44a9a0d)

  • Merge pull request #1221 from HL7/jd-ratiorange (44a5358)
